###############################################################################
# OBJECTIVE
###############################################################################
Comprehensive analysis of old iOS and Android applications to extract complete API
implementation patterns, parameters, request structures, and optimization techniques.

###############################################################################
# REQUIREMENTS
###############################################################################
requirements:
  - Analyze old iOS app API implementation (Swift code)
  - Analyze old Android app API implementation (if available)
  - Document all API endpoints used in old apps
  - Extract complete request parameter sets for each endpoint
  - Document request headers, authentication patterns
  - Identify caching strategies and optimization techniques
  - Map old app API calls to new app equivalents
  - Create comprehensive API specification document
  - Focus on: Objects, History, Tracking, Reports, Events APIs

###############################################################################
# DELIVERABLES
###############################################################################
out: [API Analysis Document with complete old app API patterns]
done:
  - All API endpoints documented from old apps
  - Complete parameter sets extracted for each endpoint
  - Request patterns and optimizations identified
  - Mapping created between old and new app APIs
  - Document stored in sprints/63/artifacts/API-Analysis.md
ref: @old-apps/navitrack-mobile-ios; @old-apps/navitrack-mobile-android.
